      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>This collection, ca. 1836-1948, contains approximately 118
         items, including records of 
         <persname>Susie V. Shepherd</persname>. Receipts of 
         <persname>William Stephen</persname>and 
         <persname>Lucy D. Shepherd</persname>indicate that William was
         a farmer who owned land in 
         <geogname>Goochland</geogname>, 
         <geogname>Louisa</geogname>and 
         <geogname>Fluvanna</geogname>counties, 
         <geogname>Virginia</geogname>, in the mid-1800s. Of interest
         are bills from 
         <persname>M. S. Hoggard</persname>who acted as both dentist
         and blacksmith.</p>
      </scopecontent>
